            <title>[SYNAPSE-733] Conditional Router Mediator doesn&apos;t route messages based on HTTP Query parameters</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-733</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Conditional Router Mediator doesn&apos;t route messages based on HTTP Query parameters for GET requests. &lt;br/&gt;
In the following configuration, I&apos;m trying to route a message based on a http parameter but the condition never get satisfied. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Synapse Config :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;               &amp;lt;conditionalRouter&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                    &amp;lt;route&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                        &amp;lt;condition&amp;gt;                       &lt;br/&gt;
                            &amp;lt;equal source=&quot;s&quot; type=&quot;param&quot; value=&quot;test&quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                        &amp;lt;/condition&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                        &amp;lt;target sequence=&quot;send_seq&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                    &amp;lt;/route&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;/conditionalRouter&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;GET Request:&lt;br/&gt;
curl &lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8280/services/StockQuoteProxy?s=test&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8280/services/StockQuoteProxy?s=test&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;






